[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "なにこれ……すっごく大きい……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00509",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "あんたたち、これ何か分かったりする？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00510",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "いや……俺も初めて見るな。\nゴーレムの類のように見えるが",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_038_00511",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "えっ！？　動いた！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00512",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "レスナ、危ない！　下がって！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00513",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "……お待ちしておりました。錬金術士レスナ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_723_038_00514",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "！？　しゃべることができるの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_038_00515",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "案内人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "私はこの島の案内人。\nあなたを果ての大陸まで導く者です",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_723_038_00516",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "うへぇ。同業者だったんすか？\nどーも、アルビーナです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00517",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "怖い人じゃないみたい……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_038_00518",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "さて……どうだろうね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_038_00519",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "案内人さんということなら、よかったです。\nぜひ、果ての大陸まで案内をお願いできますか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00520",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "案内人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "私の問いに答えてください。\n正しく答えられれば、果ての大陸へと案内しましょう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_723_038_00521",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "問い……？　正しく答えられなかったら、\nどうなるんでしょうか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00522",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "案内人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "誤った回答を行ったときは、処理４へと移行します",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_723_038_00523",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "377912885312431765",
		"text": "処理４……？　なんなのよそれは！\nなんだか悪い予感がするわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_038_00524",
		"still_path_hash": "6764252557264005345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "まあまあ。間違えなければいいんだから。\nハンマーも振らなきゃ砕けない、だよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00525",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "簡単な問いだといいけどさ……\nとはいえ、やらないっていう選択肢はないんだけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_038_00526",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "そうですね……分かりました。\nレスナ、答えます",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00527",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "案内人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "問１",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_723_038_00528",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "案内人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "あなたの目の前に、病に侵され、苦しむ人々がいます。\nその病を癒す方法は見つかっていません",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_723_038_00529",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "案内人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "しかし、一人の命を犠牲にし、身体を調べれば、\n治療法が確立され他の人々を救うことができそうです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_723_038_00530",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "案内人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "あなたはどうしますか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_723_038_00531",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "……え？　なにこの問い？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00532",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "これまで九偉人が仕掛けてきたのと同じだよ。\nパルメ族の「管理」をレスナちゃんにさせたいんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00533",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "悪趣味な、命の選択ね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_038_00534",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "何よこれ。パルメ族の思想を受け入れないと\n正解できないじゃない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00535",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "果ての大陸をダシに、レスナにその思想を\n受け入れろって言ってるんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_038_00536",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "377912885312431765",
		"text": "まったく、最後の最後まで底意地の悪い……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_038_00537",
		"still_path_hash": "6764252557264005345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00538",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（……今や果ての大陸到達の願いは、\n　私たちだけじゃなくて、世界中の願いになっている）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00539",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（ここで“正しく”答えないと、\n　果ての大陸への手掛かりがなくなるというなら……）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00540",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（私は、言葉だけでも受け入れるべきなのかな）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00541",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "レスナちゃん！　そんな話、乗る必要ないよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00542",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "果ての大陸がどこかにあるなら、案内なんか\nされなくたって絶対たどり着けるんだから！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00543",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（その通りだ。その「選択」をしてしまったら、\n　きっと私は錬金術士として胸を張れなくなる！）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00544",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（錬金術は、\n　すべての人を幸せにするものなんだから！）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00545",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "……私は、誰の命も犠牲にするつもりはありません。\n錬金術で、全員助けてみせます！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00546",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "案内人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_723_038_00547",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "案内人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "問２",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_723_038_00548",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "案内人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "目的地へ向けて航海中、魔物に襲われ、\n船体に穴が開いたとします",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_723_038_00549",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 41,
		"localized_name": "案内人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "１０人を船外に捨てることができれば、\n無事目的地まで沈まずたどり着くことができるでしょう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_723_038_00550",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 42,
		"localized_name": "案内人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "あなたはどうしますか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_723_038_00551",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 43,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "同じことです。誰も犠牲になんてしません。\n船を直して、全員無事に目的地まで届けます",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00552",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 44,
		"localized_name": "案内人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_723_038_00553",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]